programme.title: With Sitting Bull at the Spirit Lake Massacre
programme.desc: A long-thought-lost film finally surfaces after being unseen for over eight decades. Created and copyrighted by Sunset Productions in 1925 but not released until June 15, 1927, this silent epic features the superior Native American actor Chief Yowlachie (performing here under the name Chief Yowlache) as Sitting Bull. Other fine actors in the cast include the always popular Bryant Washburn and a young Bob Steele, who appears under his real name Bob Bradbury Jr. The story takes place in the 1860s or 1870s near Spirit Lake, Iowa. Settlements of whites are growing in that region but the Sioux Indians also have professed their interest in one such settlement. Chief Sitting Bull surveys the...

programme.title: The Two Gun Man

Director Phil Rosen, whose career dated back to working with Thomas Edison and included several Charlie Chan features, keeps the action hot with help from a strong ensemble, including Charles King, Murdock MacQuarrie, and a horse named Tarzan! Maynard plays Blackie Weed, a marshall going undercover to capture and arrest some cattle rustlers.He finds himself up against some very bad men, and hes soon framed for murder. Watch as Blackie blazes his way to vindication with a .45 in either hand and the flame of righteous anger in his eyes... Kitty: Nita Martin. Joe Kearney: Lafe McKee. Lem Tolliver: Tom...

The G-Mens investigation is hindered by the distrust of the Chippewas as well as the lumbermen. Starring Russell Hayden, Jackie Coogan.

In this episode, Pat and Stoney are ordered to California to investigate reports of an anthrax epidemic and get involved in murder and a feud between neighboring ranchers. Starring Russell Hayden, Jackie Coogan.

programme.title: Stories of the Century
programme.desc: Matt and Frankie arrivein the California gold fields where Frankie is kidnapped by the infamous bandit Joaquin Murietta. Without his usualy partner, Matt enlists the help of Captain Harry Love. Starring Jim Davis, Mary Castle, and Robert Anderson. Look for Rick Jason as Murietta. Jason would later go on to star in the popular ABC war series Combat!

programme.title: Stories of the Century
programme.desc: Following the murder of a railroad agent, Matt and Frankie work to bring the vengeful Tiburcio Vasquez to justice. Starring Jim Davis, mary Castle,Anthony Caruso, Edward Colmas, Lillian Molieri, and Eddie Parker. Also, look for Glenn Strange as Sheriff Billy Rowland. Strange was known for playing Frankensteins monster in several Universal pictures, as well as a recurring role on Gunsmoke. Also, Eddie Parker, who plays a trapper in this episode, was one of Hollywoods most revered stuntmen. Directed by William Witney. Epsiode oringinally aired in 1954.

programme.title: Judge Roy Bean Collection
programme.desc: While attempting to steal land from an Indian tribe, crooked ranchers kill one of the braves. The Judge must move fast to prevent an all-out massacre. Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel, and Jackie Laughery.

programme.title: Judge Roy Bean Collection
programme.desc: In Family Ties, Judge Bean comes to the aid of the Peralta family as unscrupulous real estate agents try to force them off their land. Theyve learned that a railroad will need the property and they intend to make an undeserved profit. Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.desc: Recently released from prison, Vic Carver, and his brother Johnny, searches for Annies Uncle Luke to enact revenge. Annie successfully gets her uncle out of town, but an angry Vic kidnaps Tagg. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy Award in 1955.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.desc: With the help of Annie and Lofty, Clay Griffin, a lawman whose eyesight is deteriorating, confronts Johnny Storm and the Murdocks after they are involved in a robbery. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1955.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: Hawkeye and Chingachcook come across a group of settlers trapped in the Hurons territory.Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingachcook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild. Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper. Episode originally aired in 1957.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: Hawkeye teams up with Benjamin Franklin to take down a tyrant.Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingacchook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild. Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper. Episode originally aired in 1957.

programme.title: Bonanza
programme.desc: Little Joes date, Jennifer, is abducted and held for ransom at the circus. He and Hoss search the circus for her, facing a tough crowd of carnies in their search.Starring Michael Landon as Joe, Dan Blocker as Hoss, Lorne Green as Ben, and Pernell Roberts as Adam. This beloved western drama ran for 14 seasons on NBC. Created by David Dortort.

programme.title: Texas Brooklyn and Heaven
programme.desc: When Eddie Tayloe (Guy Madison, 5 Against the House) receives $6,000 from his grandfather, he decides to leave his drab newspaper job and move to New York. His dream is to have a play produced on Broadway. Along the way he picks up a pretty hitchhiker (Diana Lynn, The Miracle of Morgans Creek) who is also leaving her own dreary life for a shot at New York. Unfortunately, they find that the Big Apple is a hard place to make a living. But its also a city where circumstances keep bringing them together!

programme.title: Colorado Sundown
programme.desc: Murder among ranchers is the subject of this Republic Pictures drama. Starring such names as Rex Allen, Slim Pickins, and Chester Clute, this feature was directed by William Whitney. For Trivia Buffs: At one time Whitney was known as the youngest director in Hollywood, having been hired by the newly formed Republic Pictures at the tender age of 21.

programme.title: Captain Apache (Edited Version)
programme.desc: After Harry T. Collier, a beloved commissioner of Indian Affairs, is murdered in late March during the1880s, Captain Apache, an Indian graduate of West Point, is assigned by the army to investigate the crime. Suspecting that O.J., the sheriff of a town bordering the reservation may be involved in the killing, Apache travels there and finds the sheriff dining with his mistress Maude at the Paradise Saloon. Before Apache can question him, however, O.J. abruptly departs and rides out of town with Apache in pursuit. When Apache apprehends him, O.J. swears that he did not kill Collier and relates that the agents dying words were April Morning. Meanwhile, Griffin, a wealthy landowner and six of...

programme.title: Under California Stars
programme.desc: Disaster strikes when Roy Rogerss beloved horse Trigger is stolen and held for ransom money. Will Roy find $100,000 to get his faithful companion back, or will he find a way to trap the gang holding the horse hostage? Along with Roy and Trigger, youll find Andy Devine as Cookie Bullfincher, and young Michael Chapin as Ted Carver, a gallant boy who helps reunite Roy with the smartest horse in show business!

programme.title: The Star Packer
programme.desc: He Dared Death In The Outlaws Lair! John Travers (John Wayne) takes on a mysterious gang leader known as The Shadow in this vintage western from Hollywoods Poverty Row. Director/writer Robert N. Bradbury (Blue Steel, Riders of Destiny) gets the best of a remarkable cast that includes George Gabby Hayes. Of interest to film buffs is that the feature was shot in various California locations by Oscar winning cinematographer Archie Stout (The Quiet Man).

programme.title: Courageous Avenger
programme.desc: Gold, gangs, and the heroic fight for life! Johnny Mack Brown (Billy the Kid, Coquette) stars in this western thriller about murders going on in a mining community. Its a story full of twists, where the greed for gold is only surpassed by the struggle for life!

programme.title: Daughter of the West
programme.desc: A FLAMING PAGE FROM AMERICAN HISTORY Becomes a powerful motion picture...set against the panoramic grandeur of the West!. Martha Vickers stars as Lolita Moreno, a convent raised woman in the 1880s who learns about her Native American heritage through her relationship with an educated Navajo. Morena had been raised at a California mission, but when she leaves to teach school in Arizona, the threads of her mysterious past are revealed. This leads to her involvement with some dangerous people, and a chance to find love in the most unexpected way. The cast includes Phillip Reed, Donald Woods, William Farnum and Milton Kibbee. Pedro de Cordobaa stars as Chief Wykomas.

programme.title: Raiders of Old California
programme.desc: The end of the Mexican-American War finds a brazen U.S. Calvary captain and his men taking over a Spanish land grant. Albert C. Gannaway (The Badge of Marshall Brennan) directs an all-star cast including Jim Davis (Jock Ewing of Dallas), Arleen Whelan (Young Mr. Lincoln) and Lee Van Cleef (The Good, The Bad, and the Ugly). Also, look for appearances by legendary country and western stars Marty Robbins and Faron Young.

programme.title: Red Ryder: Roll, Thunder, Roll!
programme.desc: Red Ryder finds two silver conchas, the trademark of bandit El Conejo, at a raided ranch. He reports the raid to Marshal Bill Faugh but tells him that he suspects that El Conejo, a Robin Hood type character, is being framed.

programme.title: Revenge of the Virgins (Edited Version)
programme.desc: The angry and topless female members of a Native American prepare for battle when white treasure hunters move in on their sacred ground. Peter Perry Jr. (The Secret Sex Lives of Romeo and Juliet) directed this early nudie-cutie from a script by legendary cult filmmaker Ed Wood (Plan Nine from Outer Space). Writing under the pen name Peter LaRoche, Wood churned out this screenplay just before he reinvented himself as the author of seedy adult novels.

programme.title: Stagecoach to Denver
programme.desc: Ride the outlaws highway! Allan Rocky Lane stars as Red Ryder, shootin and fightin his way to justice in this old slugfest from Republic Pictures. This time hes a stagecoach driver battling a crooked land commissioner and his cohorts, including a sheriff on the take. Robert Blake costars as Little Beaver!

programme.title: Abilene Town
programme.desc: Ablaze with guns and guts and glory! Randolph Scott headlines as a star studded cast in this yarn about battling homesteaders. Director Edwin L. Marin (Tall in the Saddle) spins this dramatic post-Civil War tale that takes place in the legendary cow town of Abilene, Kansas, coaxing fine performances from the likes of Ann Dvorak, Edgar Buchanan, Thonda Fleming, and Lloyd Bridges. Saddle up and hang on!

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men
programme.desc: Pat and Stoney are ordered to San Pablo, Mexico, to find out whats behind the trouble an American tungsten mine is having. When they arrive, they discover the mine has been closed, the wells are all poisoned and the town is in the grip of a malaria epidemic. To make matters worse, the lawmen have been followed by four gunslingers determined to give the American troubleshooters all the trouble they can handle - and more. Russell Hayden stars.

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men
programme.desc: Pat Gallagher and his sidekick Stoney Crockett are Secret Service agents in the Old West, dispatched by the government to investigate crimes threatening the young nation. In this episode, Pat and Stoney tangle with a gang of robbers who have hijacked an Army payroll. Starring Russell Hayden, Jackie Coogan. Originally aired on NBC.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.desc: Uncle Joe tries to convince two rich women that Shady Rest is a farm. Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Directed by Guy Scarpitta..Series created by Paul Henning. Episode first aried in February of 1964.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.sub-title: S01 : E21 The Very Old Antique
programme.desc: Homer Bedloe (Charles Lane) tries to sell the Cannonball to a rich man as an antique.Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Directed by Jean Yarbrough. Series created by Paul Henning. Episode first aired in 1964.

programme.title: Cisco Kid
programme.desc: Cisco and Pancho are falsely accused of robbing a stagecoach. Starring Duncan Renaldo as The Cisco Kid, and Leo Carillo as Pancho. This weekly adventure series was a favorite of the 1950s, following two pals as they traveled the old west, righting wrongs and helping the underdog. The show was produced by ZIV Television, the same company that gave us Highway Patrol and Sea Hunt, and was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1951. This episode aired in 1951.

programme.title: Cisco Kid
programme.desc: Two bandits impersonate Cisco and Pancho, sending the two to prison for robbery and murder. Starring Duncan Renaldo as The Cisco Kid, and Leo Carillo as Pancho. This weekly adventure series was a favorite of the 1950s, following two pals as they traveled the old west, righting wrongs and helping the underdog. The show was nominated for a PrimeTime Emmy Award in 1951. It was produced by ZIV Television, the same company that gave us Highway Patrol and Sea Hunt. This episode aired in 1950.

programme.title: Stories of the Century
programme.desc: Jim Davis stars as Matt Clark, a railroad detective who chases outlaws preying on the railroads of the west. In this episode he has to deal with the legendary Chief Crazy Horse (George Keymas) Also starring Mary Castle, Chubby Johnson, John Holland, and Alma Beltran. Directed by William Witney. Episode originally aired in 1954.

programme.title: Stories of the Century
programme.desc: Detectives Matt and Frankie track down Black Bart, a famous criminal responsible for a string of stage coach robberies. .Starring Jim Davis and Mary Castle.Also starring Arthur Space, Sammy Ogg, Marc Hamilton, Frank Sully, and I. StanfordJjolly. Directed by William Witney. Episode first aired in 1954. Produced by B movie veteran Edward J. White.Series won an Emmy in 1955.

programme.title: Judge Roy Bean Collection
programme.desc: In this episode, crooks posing as newspapermen attempt to blackmail a local rancher in order to steal his land and property. Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel, and Jackie Laughery.

programme.title: Judge Roy Bean Collection
programme.desc: Judge Roy Bean endeavors to exact justice in the small town of Langtry in the Old West. Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel, and Jackie Laughery. In this episode, Judge Bean discovers that a young vagabond he jailed for a minor offense may be involved in a major unsolved gold heist.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.desc: After raising money for charity with a circus sideshow, Annie and Tagg are robbed of their money by a man named the Welshman. Annie and Lofty set up a trap with one last performance. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1955.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.sub-title: S01 : E24 Annie Makes a Marriage
programme.desc: Annie tries to help an ex-convict prove his innocence so that he can be with the woman he loves. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This entertaining western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1955.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: Townspeople discriminate against a young Indian doctor. Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingacchook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild. Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper. Episode originally aired in 1957.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: Hawkeye and Chingachcook set out to prove the innocence of the Delaware tribe. Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingachcook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild. Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper.Episode originally aired in 1957.

programme.title: Bonanza
programme.desc: Gunnar, a long-lost relative of the Cartwright family, arrives in Ponderosa, where the family takes him in for the night. Unknown to the Cartwrights, however, is Gunnars leading of The Comancheros, a dangerous band of criminals. After Little Joe and his girlfriend are kidnapped by The Comancheros, the Cartwrights and Gunnar must work things out.Starring Michael Landon as Joe, Dan Blocker as Hoss, Lorne Green as Ben, and Pernell Roberts as Adam. This beloved western drama ran for 14 seasons on NBC. Created by David Dortort.

programme.title: The Gay Cavalier
programme.desc: The Cisco Kid, along with Pancho, try to help an unhappy bride.

programme.title: Boots and Saddles
programme.desc: When a young Englishman inherits a ranch, none other than Gene Autry takes up the challenge of turning the Brit into a real westerner. He convinces the Brit to use the ranch to raise horses, but things quickly grow complicated. Look for the usual cast of characters from Republic Pictures, including Smiley Burnette (as the irresistible Frog Millhouse!). Songs include Take Me Back To My Boots and Saddle, and Ridin the Range.

programme.title: Enemy of the Law
programme.desc: Tex Ritter stars in this western drama about a man who goes undercover to befriend a convict believed to have stolen a shipment of government gold. Also starring Guy Wilkerson as Panhandle Perkins, this offering from Hollywoods Poverty Row features the usual fistfights and entertaining storyline that made these modestly budgeted features well worth watching. Songs include Teach Me To Forget and You Will Have to Pay both sung by Tex!

programme.title: Cry Blood Apache (Edited Version)
programme.desc: An Apache brave seeks vengeance on a band of sadistic gold hunters in this bloody drive-in western. Pitcalin (Jody McRae) leads the marauders who wipe out an Apache camp when they discover gold, only to watch their violent deeds lead to their own demise. Featuring a superb cast that also includes Dan Kemp, Robert Tessier, and Joel McRae, this coldblooded western tale was directed by character actor and filmmaker Jack Starrett (Cleopatra Jones, The Losers).

programme.title: Colorado
programme.desc: Theres trouble out west! Its the Civil War and the Union needs troops back east to defend itself. Roy Rogers stars as Lieutenant Jerry Burke, who is sent to investigate why the returning troops are being stalled in Colorado. Also starring Gabby Hayes, Pauline Moore, and Milburn Stone, this film is action packed with a turn you wont see coming!

programme.title: The Trail Beyond
programme.desc: Rod Drew (John Wayne) is in search of a missing miner and his daughter in this Lone Star Picture. Along the way, Drew rescues his pal Wabbi (Noah Beery Jr.) from card cheats who have framed him for murder. Youll find plenty of action and suspense in this vintage horse opera, originally distributed by the kings of the B western, Monogram Pictures!

programme.title: Death Valley
programme.desc: A love story and a search for gold in the Valley of Death! Dubbed simple, powerful and dramatic by the New York Times on the date of its release, Death Valley is indeed an elegant depiction of love and deception in the American desert during the Gold Rush. In what was to be the final film of famed silent film director Paul Powell (Polyanna), a cast of mostly unknown actors produces uniformly excellent work. Lyrical and graceful, Powells film spins the tale of a young boy who finds love and gold, only to have it stolen from him.

programme.title: High Lonesome
programme.desc: A young drifter is suspected of murder in this stirring production from writer/director Alan Le May (best known for writing The Searchers). John Drew Barrymore stars as Cooncat, a troubled young man who has to steal to survive. With no friends in West Texas, he falls in with some bad customers who involve him in some terrible crimes. The strong cast includes Chill Wills, Jack Elam, and John Archer, with cinematography by Oscar winner W. Howard Greene.

programme.title: Number 1 Pastor
programme.desc: AMCOP Exclusive Movie. Eze was not called by God, but by money when he realizes how much money pastors are making. He decides to venture into the ministry, guising as a pastor, and develops a plan to get money. He plants listening devices in the houses of his church members and pretending to prophesy what he listens in on. His ministry grows big but he soon catches the attention of Shalewa , a young investigative journalist who is desperate for her big break and she decides to do a piece on him.

programme.title: Lurk
programme.desc: A woman dedicated to her work is unaware that she has made enemies who would stop at nothing to see her dead.

programme.title: Enemy Closer
programme.desc: The relationship between Muna and Owen falls apart when Muna discovers that Owen is having an affair. The betrayal cuts her so deep, she decides to take drastic action leading to fatal consequences.

programme.title: Lama
programme.desc: When a doctor meets a patient with mysterious injuries, he suspects she is a victim of domestic abuse and asks the police to investigate putting her in even more danger.

programme.title: Broken Glass
programme.desc: AMCOP Exclusive Movie. When lke is released from prison after being convicted for a crime he didnt commit, he finds out that all his properties are gone, his wife is now married to his best friend, and a daughter that barely recognises him. Determined to get his life back, he starts a lowly job that leads him to a young woman, who feels sorry for him and decides to help him get all he has lost.

programme.title: Anger Of Death
programme.desc: A priest, known for his outspokenness, is faced with the challenge of standing up for his people through his prominent position.

programme.desc: AMC Red Carpet moments which brings you exclusive red carpet interviews with Nollywood stars at the premieres of top Nollywood movies and other industry events such as award ceremonies.

programme.desc: Following the lives of a group of young people living in a face-me-I-face-you estate. Toke is constantly putting pressure on Femi for a better life, from him getting a better job, to having children and even for him to stop flirting with his friend, Chioma.

programme.title: Excuse Me
programme.desc: The life of a successful journalist gets complicated when her love life is entangled in a news story that can make or break her career.

programme.title: Perfect Crime
programme.desc: To the outside world, Brenda and Toby seem like a loving couple until little secrets she is keeping from her family start to unravel, leading to fatal consequences.

programme.title: Reform
programme.desc: Two detectives are forced to team up with a sinister criminal to save the daughter of an important man. Can they put their differences aside for the mission?
A serial killer is on the loose and with time running out, Sam, the lead investigator on the case, will stop at nothing to catch them before they commit their next murder.

programme.title: Elenas Woe
programme.desc: A pregnant woman lady is abandoned by her ex and forced to find a living, little did she know that its all a ploy for her downfall, as she finds out her best friend and lovers were lovers and cohorts in duping and scamming various families.

programme.title: For Better For Trouble
programme.desc: Tensions rise in the household of a newly married couple when the husband brings home an uncouth maid.

programme.title: In The Pursuit of Love
programme.desc: In his quest to find true love, a young CEO decides to disguise himself and hide his true identity. He meets a female who challenges his whole idea of love and hustle. Will this be his final bus stop?

programme.title: Stood Up
programme.desc: AMCOP Exclusive Movie. On the day of her wedding to Patrick, Roselyn receives a message from him telling her that he would not be showing up as he can no longer marry her. Heartbroken, she reluctantly rekindles her relationship with Walter, her ex boyfriend, who she broke up with because of his cult ties. Walter convinces Roselyn he is no longer in a cult, and they soon make plans to marry, however the unexpected happens a night to their wedding.

programme.title: The Governors Daughter
programme.desc: AMCOP Exclusive Movie. A high-flying woman, Mrs. Helen Onoja, is fixated on making sure her only son, Felix, not only marries from a class as high as hers, but specifically a governor’s daughter. She goes all out to arrange for him to date the spoilt daughter of her childhood friend, whose father happens to be the incumbent governor of Kogi State, ignoring the fact that Felix is in love with another woman, Abike. Meanwhile Felix’s relationship with Abike suffers because he is unable to stand up to his domineering mother.

programme.title: Fatman
programme.desc: Vinksahtaneessa nykymaailmassa Joulupukki on todella olemassa ja vararikossa, koska lapset ovat enimmakseen tuhmia eika valtiolta heru tukea tyovoimakuluihin kysynnan laskiessa. Joulupukki on ryypiskeleva, asetta heilutteleva pahis, koska kun lentelee ympari maailmaa, joku voi joskus ampua.

programme.title: Nothing Like the Holidays
programme.desc: Tassa lamminhenkisessa joulukomediassa Rodriguezin perheen kauempana asuvat jasenet kokoontuvat vanhempiensa kotiin kenties viimeista kertaa viettamaan joulua yhdessa.

programme.title: 12 Gifts of Christmas
programme.desc: Tyoton taidemaalari Anna kamppailee taloutensa kanssa, mutta loytaa tyopaikan kirean liikemiehen Marcin henkilokohtaisena jouluostosten tekijana.

programme.title: Furry Little Christmas
programme.desc: Suurkaupungin elainlaakari kaatuu pikkukaupungin laakariin, kun tama paattaa jarjestaa New Yorkin joulun hanen kotikaupungissaan Vermontissa.

programme.title: Joulu tilauksesta
programme.desc: Gretchen saa joulun tapahtua missa ja milloin tahansa.

programme.title: Silent Night: A Song for the World
programme.desc: Maailman kuuluisimman joululaulun syntytarina. Dokumenttielokuva kertoo, miten nuori Joseph Mohr paatyi kirjoittamaan vuonna 1818 ensiesityksensa saaneen laulun "Jouluyo, juhlayo".

programme.title: Maanviljelija ja Belle Pelastavat Joulumaan
programme.desc: Kun kuuluisa malli palaa pikkukaupunkiinsa juuri ennen joulua - han tapaa lapsuudenystavansa, jolla on nyt nuori tytar ja maatila. Pian kipinat lentavat heidan valillaan - ja han alkaa oppia, etta rakkaus ja kauneus tulevat sisalta. Kaupunki on vaarassa menettaa rakkaan Joulumaan festivaalinsa. He huomaavat, etta ihmeita voi tapahtua paattavaisyydella ja uskolla.

programme.title: Mr. Christmas
programme.desc: Tom on luonut uran auttamalla asiakkaita, jotta nama loytaisivat rakastetulleen taydellisen lahjan. Joulun lahestyessa Tomin paras ystava Paul pyytaa Tomia keksimaan lahjan tyttoystavalleen Jennylle. Kun Tom tutustuu Jennyyn paremmin, asia mutkistuu, koska han huomaa rakastuneensa kaverinsa tyttoystavaan. Tyotehtava on melkein hoidettu, mutta Tom on pahoillaan, koska hanen ainoa mahdollisuutensa loytaa sielunkumppani on kariutumassa.

programme.title: Perheella on Valia Joulu
programme.desc: Joulu on kaikkea muuta kuin tavallinen - kun kolme kinastelevaa sisarusta uusperheesta - eivat ole samaa mielta. Nuorin viimeistelee vuosittaista tiedeprojektiaan - ja kutsuu vahingossa joulun henkea. He heraavat ja huomaavat, etta heidan kehonsa ovat vaihtuneet, eivatka he voi muuttua takaisin, ennen kuin he oppivat viettamaan joulun yhdessa rakastavana perheena.

programme.title: Santa Who?
programme.desc: Oikea joulupukki putoaa reesta ja menettaa muistinsa. Han tormaa pian tympaantyneeseen TV-toimittajaan, joka on hanen ainoa toivonsa palauttaa muisti ajoissa, etta joulu voidaan pelastaa.

programme.title: Puppy Star Christmas
programme.desc: Pup Star -perhe on kasvanut! Uusien pentujen, Cindyn, Rosien, Charlien ja Brodyn tulee oppia, mita joulu oikeasti tarkoittaa. Kun Pup Starin pahikset juonivat pilaavansa joulun, pennut paatyvat pohjoisnavalle pelastamaan joulupukin ja jouluhengen. Heidan seikkailunsa on taynna uusia pentumaisia lauluja, jotka levittavat joulun riemua vuoden ympari.

programme.title: Tonttumies
programme.desc: Joulupukki jattaa tontun pelastamaan Harperin perheen kurjalta joululta. Tonttu perheineen saa enemman kuin toivoi, kun lapset auttavat tonttua loytamaan voimansa - ja identiteettinsa orastavana supersankarina.

programme.title: Deck the Halls
programme.desc: Menestysmysteerikirjailija Mary Higgins Clarkin romaaniin perustuva elokuva nahdaan jouluna salapoliisitarinana. Naisetsiva lyottaytyy yksiin amatoorietsivan kanssa loytaakseen kadonneen isansa.

programme.title: A Christmas in Royal Fashion
programme.desc: Kansainvalisen PR-yrityksen kaunis ja lahjakas assistentti Kristin Cooper saa vastuulleen vaatealalla tyoskentelevan liikemies Carsonin vuotuisen joulun muotinaytoksen ja huutokaupan jarjestamisen.

programme.title: The Loss Adjuster
programme.desc: En forsikringsmann som kjemper med tap og kjærlighet, oppdager nye muligheter i en uke full av uventede hendelser og komiske vendepunkter.

programme.title: A Merry Holiday
programme.desc: Menestyva suunnittelija Christy stressaa saadakseen ison toimeksiannon. Han saa avukseen Jonathanin, joka yrittaa koristella poikamiesasuntoaan talven ihmemaaksi tehdakseen vaikutuksen tyttoystavansa isaan. Yhteistyo alkaa huonosti, mutta pian he tajuavat, etta heidan on pakko jatkaa ja auttaa toisiaan. Mutta mita enemman he viettavat aikaa yhdessa, sita rennommin he suhtautuvat toisiinsa. Ehka yhdessa viihtyminen ei johdukaan enaa vain tyosta.

programme.title: Tyler Perrys a Madea Christmas
programme.desc: Madea juhlistaa joulua yhdessa ystavansa ja taman maalla asuvan perheen kanssa. Nyt on parasta olla kilttina!

programme.title: Joulukuponki
programme.desc: Entinen luistelumestari alkaa opettaa ystavansa lammella- ja jakaa "kuponkeja" houkutellakseen uusia oppilaita. Kun hanen entinen lukiorakkaansa (ja nyt kuuluisa jaakiekkoilija)- tuo veljentyttarensa tunneille, vanhat liekit syttyvat uudelleen- ja joulu on taynna uutta mahdollisuutta rakkauteen.

programme.title: Joulukuppikakkuja
programme.desc: Kun perheen leipomo joutuu ehka sulkemaan ovensa ennen joulua - siskokset Kimin ja Ginan on lyottaydyttava yhteen - kansallisessa leivontakilpailussa voittaakseen paapalkinnon. Kilpailijoiden ja tikittavan kellon maailmassa - tarvitaan joulun ihme leipomon pelastamiseksi. He saattavat loytaa paljon suuremman palkinnon kuin toivoivat.

programme.title: Ihme Joulujarvella
programme.desc: Kun teinipoika menettaa parhaan ystavansa ja isansa joulun aikaan- han jattaa lempilajinsa jaakiekon ja hylkaa ystavansa. Kun jaakaukalo ilmestyy jaatyneelle jarvelle hanen kotinsa lahelle, han muistelee hyvia aikoja.

programme.title: Santa Who?
programme.desc: Oikea joulupukki putoaa reesta ja menettaa muistinsa. Han tormaa pian tympaantyneeseen TV-toimittajaan, joka on hanen ainoa toivonsa palauttaa muisti ajoissa, etta joulu voidaan pelastaa.

programme.title: 12 Joulukoiraa: Suuri koiranpentupelastus
programme.desc: Dovervillen lapset kilpailevat aikaa ja mahdottomia todennakoisyyksia vastaan- pelastaakseen koiraorpokodin haikailemattomalta pohatalta.

programme.title: A Winter Princess
programme.desc: Hienon gaalan jalkeen prinsessa Carly paattaa pitaa sapattivuoden ja aloittaa unelmatyon hiihtokeskuksessa. Yksikaan uusista tyotovereista ei tieda, kuka han oikeasti on. Mutta kun kuninkaallisen suvun jasenia ilmestyy hiihtokeskukseen, salaisuutta on pian hyvin vaikea sailyttaa paljastumatta. Samalla valmistellaan keskuksen 50-vuotisjuhlia ja Carly huomaa ihastuneensa omistajan veljeen Jesseen. Carlyn taytyy tehda suuria paatoksia elamassaan ja han tuntee olevansa yha enemman ymmallaan.

programme.title: Tyler Perrys a Madea Christmas
programme.desc: Madea juhlistaa joulua yhdessa ystavansa ja taman maalla asuvan perheen kanssa. Nyt on parasta olla kilttina!

programme.title: Another Christmas Coincidence
programme.desc: Toisilleen tuntemattomat Alice ja Jack, joilla on taysin erilainen tausta, paatyvat sattumalta samoihin viikonloppuhaihin. He pitavat heti toisistaan, mutta Alice arkailee uutta suhdetta, koska entinen kaukosuhde paattyi ikavasti. Alice alkaa kuitenkin Olga-aidin rohkaisemana tottua vahitellen ajatukseen deittailun aloittamisesta. Uudet yhteensattumat lahentavat nuoria toisiinsa, samalla kun tielle osuu yha uusia esteita, jotka vaikeuttavat juuri alkanutta romanssia.

programme.desc: Tyoton leski-isa lahettaa tyttarensa tatinsa luo kaupunkiin- joka on kieltanyt koirat. Matkalla kouluun han loytaa koiranpennun ja paattaa pitaa sen - vaikka rankkuri on hanen kannoillaan. Hanen pitaa selvittaa, mita koirille tapahtuu- ja hurmata pormestari ikimuistoisimmalla joulunaytelmalla.

programme.title: Arvottomat
programme.desc: Mika Kaurismaen ensimmainen pitka elokuva. Kasikirjoituksen han teki yhdessa veljensa Akin kanssa. Arvottomat on ajaton kuvaus siita kuinka Pikkurikollinen Manne, maalaispoika Harri ja kaunis Veera ajavat Volgalla lapi katoavien suomalaismaisemien, poliisien ja gangsterien roikkuessa herkeamatta kintereilla.. Vauhdikasta matkaa siivittavat mm. Juicen ja Rauli Baddingin ikivihreat kappaleet.

programme.title: Alena
programme.desc: Kun Alena saapuu uuteen eliittisisaoppilaitokseen, Filippa ja muut tytot alkavat kiusata hanta. Mutta Alenan paras ystava Josefin ei anna hanen ottaa vastaan enaa yhtaan loylytysta. Ellei Alena itse taistele vastaan, Josefin tekee sen hanen puolestaan. Rajusti.

programme.title: Ohjelmat jatkuvat pian
programme.desc: Olemme pienilla kauneusunilla! Katso lisaa Rakuten TV:n tarjoamaa ilmaisviihdetta.

programme.title: Odd Man Rush
programme.desc: Odd Man Rush perustuu Bill Keenanin humoristiseen muistelmateokseen, josta tuli jymymenestys. Harvardin latkajoukkueen Bobby Sanders siirtyy pelaamaan Ruotsin alemmille sarjatasoille diilissa, johon liittyy mm. laadukas pesukone. Ruotsissa romanttinen suhde paikalliseen tyttoon pakottaa miehen pohtimaan tarkemmin seka elamaa yleensa etta lapsuuden haavetta NHL:ssa pelaamisesta.

programme.title: A Polar Year
programme.desc: 28-vuotias Anders paattaa matkata Gronlantiin ja ryhtya opettajaksi pienessa kylassa. Hanen vanhempansa ottavat asiaan etaisyytta, silla he olettavat taman ottavan kotitilan haltuunsa, mutta Anders kaipaa maisemanvaihdosta ja uusia haasteita. Elama pienessa kylassa on kovaa – kovempaa kuin Anders oli olettanut. Kylalaiset eivat lampene tulokkaalle, ja mikali han aikoo olla asukkaille – varsinkin lapsille – lainkaan hyodyksi, on hanen tehtava tarkea paatos. Hanen on opittava tuntemaan ihmiset, opeteltava kylan tavoille ja varsinkin tuntea sen perinteet. Vasta sitten aivan uusi maailma aukenee Andersin edessa...

programme.title: Hamlet liikemaailmassa
programme.desc: Maailmankirjallisuuden tunnetuin sukudraama on siiretty nykysuomen liike-elaman vallan linnakkeisiin, keskelle Helsingin rock´n rollin tahdissa sykkivaa betoniviidakkoa.

programme.title: Cha Cha Cha
programme.desc: Siltojen alla asusteleva alkoholisti Matti (Matti Pellonpaa) on saamassa Amerikan tadiltaan huomattavan perinnon, mutta miehen tulisi olla edustuskelpoinen tadin vierailun ajan. Matti kertoo tilanteesta autokauppiaana tyoskentelevalle ystavalleen, joka ehdottaa korvausta vastaan roolien vaihtoa.

programme.title: Leningrad Cowboys go America
programme.desc: Leningrad Cowboys Go America kertoo maailman huonoimman rock-yhtyeen matkasta Siperian tundralta Yhdysvaltojen kautta Meksikoon despoottisen managerinsa Vladimirin (Matti Pellonpaa) johdolla. Elokuvasta sukeutui kansainvalinen menestys ja se nosti Leningrad Cowboys -yhtyeen maailmanmaineeseen.

programme.title: Bitchkram
programme.desc: Kristin laskee paivia ylioppilaskirjoituksiin, jolloin han vihdoin voi jattaa pikkukaupungin ja manipuloivan sisarensa unelmiensa New Yorkia varten. Kaikki on taydellista, ja paikallislehti on luvannut julkaista Kristinin kolumneja kaupungista, joka ei koskaan nuku. Mutta Kristin myohastyy lennoltaan ja piiloutuu sen sijaan Andrean, omituisen nuoren tyton, luo syrjaiseen maalaistaloon valttaakseen taydellisen noyryytyksen.

programme.title: Tulitikkutehtaan tytto
programme.desc: Äitinsa ja isapuolensa kanssa asuva ja tulitikkutehtaan liukuhihnalla tyoskenteleva Iiris (Kati Outinen, Mies vailla menneisyytta ja Le Havre) erehtyy luulemaan tanssiravintolassa kohtaamansa miehen kanssa viettamaansa yota rakkaudeksi. Vaarinkasityksella on kohtalokkaat seuraukset.

programme.title: Leningrad Cowboys Meet Moses
programme.desc: Leningrad Cowboys Go American itsenainen jatko-osa kertoo Meksikon takamaille juuttuneen orkesterin kunniattomasta mutta varikkaasta matkasta takaisin Siperian laajoille aroille tuomisinaan vain ylpeytensa seka Vapauden patsaalta niistetty nena.

programme.title: Total Balalaika Show
programme.desc: Toinen maailmansota paattyi lopullisesti vasta kesakuussa 1993 kun Leningrad Cowboys ja Puna-armeijan kuoro esiintyivat yhdessa Helsingin Senaatintorilla jarjestetyssa konsertissa 70 000 katsojan edessa.

programme.title: Mies vailla menneisyytta
programme.desc: Mies vailla menneisyytta kertoo muistinsa menettavasta miehesta, joka aloittaa elamansa alusta yhteiskunnan koyhimpien keskella. Mies vailla menneisyytta sai Cannesin elokuvajuhlien Grand Prix -palkinnon ja Kati Outinen (Tulitikkutehtaan tytto ja Le Havre) palkittiin roolisuorituksestaan parhaan naisnayttelijan palkinnolla. Elokuvan miespaaosassa nahdaan Markku Peltola (Jadesoturi ja Kauas pilvet karkaavat).

programme.title: Juha
programme.desc: Juha (Sakari Kuosmanen, Kauas pilvet karkaavat) ja Marja (Kati Outinen, Sauna) elavat yhdessa onnellisina ja viattomina kuin lapset kunnes kaarme luikertelee paratiisiin Shemeikan (Andre Wilms, Boheemielamaa) hahmossa. Juha perustuu Juhani Ahon kuuluisaan romaaniin. Se on myos 1900-luvun viimeinen mykkaelokuva. Musiikin elokuvaan on saveltanyt Anssi Tikanmaki.

programme.title: Paperitahti
programme.desc: Paperitahti pohjautuu tositapahtumiin. On valokuvamalli, hanen kolme miestaan, leveaa elamaa, hyvaksikayttoa, ja julkista ryopytysta.. Anna (Pirkko Hamalainen) on ex-missi, nykyinen huippumalli, jonka elama ajautuu syoksykierteeseen miesten takia. Anna joutuu vahitellen seka hamaraperaisen liikemiehen, Ulfin (Hannu Lauri), etta alkoholisoituneen ja vakivaltaisen valokuvaajan, Iljan (Kari Vaananen), hyvaksikayton kohteeksi. Ainoaksi oikeaksi ystavaksi paljastuu elamaan rohkeasti suhtautuva Taukka (Matti Rasila). Anna paattaa koettaa paeta elamansa pahoja asioita, mutta se vaatii rohkeita paatoksia ja valmiutta maksamaan niiden hinta.

programme.title: Arvottomat
programme.desc: Mika Kaurismaen ensimmainen pitka elokuva. Kasikirjoituksen han teki yhdessa veljensa Akin kanssa. Arvottomat on ajaton kuvaus siita kuinka Pikkurikollinen Manne, maalaispoika Harri ja kaunis Veera ajavat Volgalla lapi katoavien suomalaismaisemien, poliisien ja gangsterien roikkuessa herkeamatta kintereilla.. Vauhdikasta matkaa siivittavat mm. Juicen ja Rauli Baddingin ikivihreat kappaleet.

programme.title: Van Veeteren - Tapaus G
programme.desc: Van Veeterenin ainoa selvittamattomaksi jaanyt tapaus nakee jalleen paivanvalon kun eraan yksityisetsivan tytar tulee tapaamaan hanta. Vakivaltainen murhaaja, joka katosi vuosia sitten jaljettomiin, vaikuttaa palanneen uudella nimella varustettuna - ja sekaantuneena uuteen murhaan. Van Veeterenilla on niin ammatillisia kuin henkilokohtaisiakin syita saattaa syyllinen telkien taa.

programme.title: Kauas pilvet karkaavat
programme.desc: Kauas pilvet karkaavat kertoo helsinkilaispariskunnasta. Raitiovaununkuljettaja ja perinteikkaan ravintola Dubrovnikin hovimestari menettavat tyonsa, mutta eivat toivoaan Aki Kaurismaen (Le Havre) Suomi-trilogian ensimmaisessa osassa.

programme.title: Rikos ja rangaistus
programme.desc: Rikos ja rangaistus on moderni tulkinta Dostojevskin kuuluisasta romaanista. Murhaajan (Markku Toikka) ja poliisin (Esko Nikkari, Mies vailla menneisyytta) huimaava psykologinen kaksintaistelu tapahtuu oisen Helsingin sivukujilla ja lain tuolla puolen.

programme.title: Mies vailla menneisyytta
programme.desc: Mies vailla menneisyytta kertoo muistinsa menettavasta miehesta, joka aloittaa elamansa alusta yhteiskunnan koyhimpien keskella. Mies vailla menneisyytta sai Cannesin elokuvajuhlien Grand Prix -palkinnon ja Kati Outinen (Tulitikkutehtaan tytto ja Le Havre) palkittiin roolisuorituksestaan parhaan naisnayttelijan palkinnolla. Elokuvan miespaaosassa nahdaan Markku Peltola (Jadesoturi ja Kauas pilvet karkaavat).

programme.title: Van Veeteren - Carambole
programme.desc: Mies tormaa autollaan 14-vuotiaaseen poikaan, joka saa surmansa valittomasti. Tapahtuma-aikana on pimeaa ja sateista, ja mies pakenee onnettomuuspaikalta. Tama on virhe, jota han tulee katumaan katkerasti, ja joka muuttaa hanen koko elamansa.Van Veeterille tama merkitsee tapausta, joka koskettaa hanta henkilokohtaisella tasolla - tapausta, joka riistaa hanelta hyvin rakkaan ihmisen.

programme.title: Munsterin juttu
programme.desc: Varakas viininmaahantuoja loydetaan brutaalisti murhattuna voimakkaan iskun jalkeen paahan. Munster saa tapauksen tutkittavakseen.

programme.title: Bitchkram
programme.desc: Kristin laskee paivia ylioppilaskirjoituksiin, jolloin han vihdoin voi jattaa pikkukaupungin ja manipuloivan sisarensa unelmiensa New Yorkia varten. Kaikki on taydellista, ja paikallislehti on luvannut julkaista Kristinin kolumneja kaupungista, joka ei koskaan nuku. Mutta Kristin myohastyy lennoltaan ja piiloutuu sen sijaan Andrean, omituisen nuoren tyton, luo syrjaiseen maalaistaloon valttaakseen taydellisen noyryytyksen.

programme.title: Total Balalaika Show
programme.desc: Toinen maailmansota paattyi lopullisesti vasta kesakuussa 1993 kun Leningrad Cowboys ja Puna-armeijan kuoro esiintyivat yhdessa Helsingin Senaatintorilla jarjestetyssa konsertissa 70 000 katsojan edessa.

programme.title: Tulitikkutehtaan tytto
programme.desc: Äitinsa ja isapuolensa kanssa asuva ja tulitikkutehtaan liukuhihnalla tyoskenteleva Iiris (Kati Outinen, Mies vailla menneisyytta ja Le Havre) erehtyy luulemaan tanssiravintolassa kohtaamansa miehen kanssa viettamaansa yota rakkaudeksi. Vaarinkasityksella on kohtalokkaat seuraukset.

programme.title: Juha
programme.desc: Juha (Sakari Kuosmanen, Kauas pilvet karkaavat) ja Marja (Kati Outinen, Sauna) elavat yhdessa onnellisina ja viattomina kuin lapset kunnes kaarme luikertelee paratiisiin Shemeikan (Andre Wilms, Boheemielamaa) hahmossa. Juha perustuu Juhani Ahon kuuluisaan romaaniin. Se on myos 1900-luvun viimeinen mykkaelokuva. Musiikin elokuvaan on saveltanyt Anssi Tikanmaki.

programme.title: Varjoja paratiisissa
programme.desc: Varjoja paratiisissa kertoo roskakuskin ja supermarketin kassan rakkaustarinan. Se kertoo ihmisista kadun varjoisalla puolella, mutta myos itsekunnioituksesta ja rakkauden valttamattomyydesta.

programme.title: Klaani - tarina Sammakoiden suvusta
programme.desc: Klaani on rikollissuvun tarina, jossa Mika Kaurismaki kasittelee perinteisen eeppisen muodon valityksella olemassaolon ehtoja, lain oikean ja vaaran puolen hailyvalla rajalla. Sammakoitten perheen nuorin poika Aleksanteri on sukunsa valkoinen lammas. Hanen toivotaan pysyvan kaidalla tiella, toisin kuin isansa ja muut suvun miehet. Mutta perhe on pahin ja veri on vetta sakeampaa.. Perhedraama Klaani on upea kunnianosoitus vanhalle Suomi-filmille. Paaosissa nahdaan Markku Halme ja Minna Soisalo ja sivuroolit vilisevat lukuisia huippunayttelijoita: Lasse Poysti, Juhani Niemela, Antti Litja, Kari Vaananen, Soli Labbart.

programme.title: Laitakaupungin valot
programme.desc: Laitakaupungin valot kertoo yovartijana tyoskentelevasta Koistisesta, joka joutuu petoksen uhriksi. Laitakaupungin valot oli mukana vuoden 2006 Cannesin elokuvajuhlien kansainvalisessa kilpasarjassa. Elokuva palkittiin parhaan elokuvan Jussi-palkinnolla vuonna 2007. Lisaksi Timo Salminen voitti Jussin parhaasta kuvauksesta ja Markku Patila parhaasta lavastuksesta.

programme.title: Rosso
programme.desc: Roadmovieta ja rikosdraamaa taidokkaasti yhdisteleva Rosso on kertomus sisilialaisesta palkkamurhaajasta Giancarlo Rossosta, joka on tullut Suomeen etsimaan seuraavaa kohdettaan, joka sattuu olemaan hanen rakastettunsa Marja. Odottamattomasti Rosso saa jaljitysapua Marjan veljelta Martilta, vaikkei heilla ole edes yhteista kielta. Matkalle mahtuu niin romuttamokeikka kuin pari ryostoakin..

programme.title: Arvottomat
programme.desc: Mika Kaurismaen ensimmainen pitka elokuva. Kasikirjoituksen han teki yhdessa veljensa Akin kanssa. Arvottomat on ajaton kuvaus siita kuinka Pikkurikollinen Manne, maalaispoika Harri ja kaunis Veera ajavat Volgalla lapi katoavien suomalaismaisemien, poliisien ja gangsterien roikkuessa herkeamatta kintereilla.. Vauhdikasta matkaa siivittavat mm. Juicen ja Rauli Baddingin ikivihreat kappaleet.

programme.title: Nicks Film Lightning Over Water
programme.desc: Wim Wendersin ohjaama dokumenttielokuva on syvaluotaava ja koskettava elokuva amerikkalaisen kulttiohjaajan, Nuori kapinallinen -elokuvasta parhaiten tunnetun Nicholas Rayn viimeisista paivista. “Tiesin, etta han halusi tehda tyota, kuolla tyonsa aareen”, Wim Wenders sanoo elokuvassa. YhteistyossaWendersin ja kuvausryhman kanssa Ray tekee kuolemastaan yhteisen projektin ja taideteoksen. Parantumattoman syovan hitaasti riuduttama Ray ei halua laitostua saattokodissa.

programme.title: Van Veeteren - Tapaus G
programme.desc: Van Veeterenin ainoa selvittamattomaksi jaanyt tapaus nakee jalleen paivanvalon kun eraan yksityisetsivan tytar tulee tapaamaan hanta. Vakivaltainen murhaaja, joka katosi vuosia sitten jaljettomiin, vaikuttaa palanneen uudella nimella varustettuna - ja sekaantuneena uuteen murhaan. Van Veeterenilla on niin ammatillisia kuin henkilokohtaisiakin syita saattaa syyllinen telkien taa.

programme.title: Leading Lady

Eika aikaakaan, kun Jodi huomaa hurmaantuneensa seka paikallisten ystavallisyydesta etta Kobuksen itsepaisyydesta enemman kuin uskaltaisi edes myontaa…

programme.title: Loves Last Resort
programme.desc: 10 vuoden seurustelun jalkeen Chloen poikaystava Eric ei ole viela kypsynyt Chloen haluamaksi mieheksi. Chloe toivoo voivansa nopeuttaa asioiden kulkua jattamalla hanet. Kuusi kuukautta myohemmin he tapaavat, ja Eric paljastaa menevansa naimisiin. Paastakseen pois kaikesta Chloe lahtee lomalle, ja samaan lomapaikkaan ilmestyy Eric tyttoystavansa kanssa.

programme.title: Almost Friends

programme.title: Lovesick

programme.title: Lahetys joulua

programme.title: Seeking a Friend for the End of the World
programme.desc: Valtava asteroidi lahestyy Maata, ja viimeinen keino sen pysayttamiseksi on juuri epaonnistunut. Ihmiset reagoivat 21 paivan paasta koittavaan maailmanloppuun varsin kirjavilla teoilla. Vakuutusmyyja Dodgen ja naapurintytto Pennyn tiet kohtaavat mellakoiden yltyessa ja he paattavat auttaa toisiaan matkalla kohti viimeisia paamaariaan.

programme.title: Jouluhaat
programme.desc: Haley Foster pakeni lapsuutensa pikkukaupungista Pineridgesta ja siirtyi suurkaupunkilaiselamaan losangelesilaisena haajarjestelijana rva Reynoldsin omistamassa eliittiluokan yrityksessa.

programme.title: Le week-end
programme.desc: Nick ja Meg, viisikymppinen brittiaviopari elaa Birminghamissa, missa Meg toimii peruskoulun biologian opettajana ja Nick epamuodikkaan yliopiston filosofian opettajana. Pariskunta suuntaa rakkauden ja romantiikan kaupunkiin, Pariisiin, viikonlopuksi puhaltaakseen vanhan kipinan uudelleen liekkeihin.

programme.title: Kesaprinssi
programme.desc: PR-kriisinhallitsija Deidre ja hanen assistenttinsa Mandy lentavat apuun, kun kapinallinen kuninkaallinen, prinssi Colin, pidatetaan idaholaisessa pikkukaupungissa. Deidren selvitellessa omaa fiaskoaan Mandy huomaa odottamattomia ura- ja romanssimahdollisuuksia.

programme.title: Bottled with Love
programme.desc: Abbey on onneton, turhautunut ja melkein toivosta luopunut uranainen, koska deittailu ei ota sujuakseen. Isoaiti ehdottaa, etta Abbey kirjoittaisi kaikki toiveensa rakkauskirjeeksi suoraan sydamestaan. Abbey noudattaa neuvoa vastahakoisesti, panee kirjeen pulloon ja heittaa sen mereen. Aika kuluu, ja kuukausia myohemmin Abbey aloittaa projektin pomonsa pojan Nickin kanssa. Nick on sattumalta loytanyt pullopostin tietamatta, etta se on Abbeyn. Mutta vahitellen han tajuaa yhdistaa kirjeen Abbeyyn. Tilanne ja salaisuus kayvat hyvin kiusalliseksi ja Nick paattaa kertoa kirjeesta. Koska Nick on salannut asiaa pitkaan, Abbey kaskee hanta painumaan hemmettiin. Mutta Nick ei vahasta saikahda.

programme.title: Intersection
programme.desc: Keskella Marokon autiomaata tapahtuu tuhoisa auto-onnettomuus. Mukana ovat haamatkaansa viettava aviopari, tuoreen vaimon salainen rakastaja, vankilaan matkalla oleva timanttisalakuljettaja saattajansa kanssa seka arvoituksellinen nainen sylissaan pieni vauva. Miten kaikkien tarinat ja menneisyys kuroutuvat lopulta yhteen ja pystyvatko he luottamaan toisiinsa selvitakseen pois aavikolta ennen kuin on liian myohaista vai saapuuko pelastus tuntemattoman miehen lahestyessa horisontissa...

programme.title: Griffin and Phoenix
programme.desc: Kun Griffin saa kuulla, etta hanella on kuolemaan johtava sairaus, han paattaa ottaa kohtalonsa omiin kasiinsa ja elaa taysilla loppuun asti. Han tapaa Phoenixin ja aikaa myoten rakastuu tahan, mutta myos Phoenixilla on salaisuus...

programme.title: They Came Together
programme.desc: Joelin (Paul Rudd) ja Mollyn (Amy Poehler) tapaaminen on vihaa ensisilmayksella: Joelin iso Corporate Candy Company uhkaa tehdan lopun Amyn omalaatuisesta karkkikaupasta. Lisaksi Joel haikailee edelleen seksikkaan exansa (Cobie Smulders) peraan. Kumma kylla he rakastuvat vain erotakseen elokuvan loppupuolella. Molly alkaa tapailla kirjanpitajaansa (Ed Helms). Mutta aivan loppuhetkilla...noh, sinun taytyy nahda se itse. (Vinkki: Joel pitaa suuren puheen ja he palaavat yhteen.) Railakas ja epakunnoittava, kumouksellinen romanttinen komedia Wet Hot American Summerin, Wanderlustin ja Role Modelsin ohjaajalta.

programme.title: The Death Of Charlie Countryman
programme.desc: Charlie Countrymanin (LaBeouf) hyvin tavallinen elama saa uuden suunnan kun han kummallisten sattumusten kautta rakastuu romanialaiseen kaunottareen Gabiin (Wood). Yhdessaolon esteeksi nousee kuitenkin Gabin tummanpuhuva menneisyys ja yltiovakivaltainen aviomies, rikollispomo Nigel (Mikkelsen). Charliella on vain yksi vaihtoehto Gabin vapauttamiseksi: pelastaa tytto ja maksaa siita hengellaan.

programme.title: Love and Honor
programme.desc: Kun nuori sotilas Vietnamissa joutuu kotikaupungin tyton kaatamaan, han ja hanen paras ystavansa paattavat menna AWOLiin ja palata osavaltioihin voittaakseen hanet takaisin.

programme.title: The Right Kind of Wrong
programme.desc: Leo Palamino on epaonnistunut kirjailija, josta tuli tiskaaja. Nyt hanet tunnetaan ex-vaimon pitamasta blogista “Miksi olet paska”, josta on tullut suuri hitti. Sitten Leo tapaa Coletten, unelmiensa naisen… paivana, jona Colette on menossa naimisiin taydellisen miehen kanssa.Peloton haaveilija Leo panee kaiken peliin nayttaakseen Colettelle ja maailmalle, mita kaikkea hyvaa on miehessa, joka tunnetaan vain huonoista puolistaan.

programme.title: You Will Meet a Tall Dark Stranger
programme.desc: Woody Allenin eloisassa ja vallattomassa elokuvassa Josh Brolin ja Naomi Watts esittavat Royta ja Sallya, joiden valjahtynyt liitto saa Sallyn rakastumaan pomoonsa ja Royn naapuritalon punamekkoiseen kaunottareen. Samaan aikaan Sallyn isa Alfie (Anthony Hopkins) hullaantuu nuoresta ilolinnusta ja hylkaa uskollisen vaimonsa

programme.desc: Pettavatko kaikki miehet? Pettavatko kaikki parit? Tassa seksikkaassa ja viekkaassa leffassa newyorkilainen galleristi Brooke ja hanen aviomiehensa Owen kohtaavat kumpikin epatavallisia houkutuksia hyvin odottamattomin seurauksin. Perustuu Kristen Lazarianin naytelmaan Push.

programme.title: Albert Nobbs
programme.desc: Albert Nobbs kertoo koskettavan tarinan 1800-luvun lopun Irlannissa, missa koyhan naisen elama on mahdotonta ilman elattajaa. Vuosikaudet Albert Nobbs on selvinnyt pukeutumalla mieheksi voidakseen tyoskennella hovimestarina Dublinin ylaluokan hotellissa. Tavatessaan hotelliin saapuvan komean maalarin, Albert havaitsee etta elama voi tarjota mahdollisuuksia myos hanen kaltaiselleen.

Kuusi vuotta myohemmin he ovat paattaneet erota, ja kumpikin haluaa ottaa rakastetun Wesley-koiran mukaansa. Asiasta ei paasta yksimielisyyteen, ja huoltajuuskiista etenee oikeuteen. Oikeus maaraa 60 paivan seurantajakson, jonka aikana tutkitaan kumpi on parempi huoltaja. Molemmat haluavat voittaa – keinoilla milla hyvansa.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E14 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 14, Portugal
programme.desc: The last chance to qualify for the World Grand Finale. Zageris and Belsak fight for the better position for the finals.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E15 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 15, Dubai World grand finals (Part 1)
programme.desc: We reach Dubai where we will crown the new champion for SCL 2016. This is part one of the world finals.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E16 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 16, Dubai World grand finals (Part 2)
programme.desc: In this last episode, the best athletes compete in Pole Push, Deadlift, Forward Hold and Loading.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E01 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 1, Norway
programme.desc: We are in beautiful Norway for the kick off of the 2017 MLO Strongman Champions League season. With partly cloudy weather and lots of snow, we have the perfect scenery for the athletes, who prepare for the first contest of the year.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E02 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 2, Germany
programme.desc: A definite highlight in this FIBO edition in Germany, Strongman Champions League introduced its new rules for a special team item. Graham Hicks tries here to set a New World Record on the biggest log in the world, currently held by Krzysztof Radzikowski. Boosted also by the presence of the acclaimed in the strongman circles names of Mark Felix and Danis Zageris.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E03 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 3, Lithuania
programme.desc: This weekend sees the Strongman Champions League Log Lift World Championships in Lithuania. Big lifting names such as Graham Hicks , Vidas Blekaitis and Vytatus Lalas are in the startlist to push some big numbers.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E04 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 4, Holland
programme.desc: The battle of the Dutch will take place this edition in Lichtenvoorde, a place very well known in Holland because of the famous “Black Cross”. The athletes will compete over six heavy events and the winner gets 25 Strongman Champions League ranking points.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E05 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 5, Serbia
programme.desc: Set in the beautiful mountain resort Zlatibor, the fifth stage of the Strongman Champions League 2017 sees 14 athletes from across the world competing for the gold medal of SCL Serbia 2017. The event welcomes top-athlete - and odds-on favourite - Matjaz Belsak (Slovenia), who has presented himself in an impressive shape so far. Can his opponents defeat him?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E06 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 6, Canada (Part 1)
programme.desc: The next two stages take place in Quebec. With eight events over two days, SCL Canada is a true ‘heavyweight’. The athletes compete in: Truck Pull, Deadlift with cars, Log Lift, and the Atlas Stones. The World’s Strongest Viking Jean-Francois Caron from Canada is a favourite, as well as current SCL leader Matjaz Belsak (Slovenia) and promising underdog Jimmy Paquet (Canada).

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E07 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 7, Canada (Part 2)
programme.desc: Welcome to the second day in Quebec. The athletes are fighting hard to win this two-day event. The last points of this SCL stage can be won over four outstanding disciplines: Power Stairs, Dumbbell Press, Keg Toss, and finally, the legendary Farmer’s Walk. Who will leave Canada with the yellow ‘Leader Shirt’?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E08 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 8, Finland (Part 1)
programme.desc: Stages 8 and 9 of the SCL are hosted in Vaasa, Finland, taking place over a spectacular two-day event. After 3 wins so far, Matjaz Belsak from Slovenia plans to extend his lead at the top of the table. Among the other 13 highly motivated strongmen, two SCL legends will make their comeback to the competition: Former World Champion of 2015, Krzysztof Radzikowski (Poland) and Dainis Zageris (Latvia).

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E09 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 9, Finland (Part 2)
programme.desc: The fight for the Finnish trophy continues. In this unmissable SCL event, the strongmen battle for the win in the Carry and Drag, the Forward Hold, Deadlifting with Cars and the Loading Race. Belsak, Radzikowski and Zageris look good after the first day, but the others haven’t given up yet.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E10 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 10, Finland Lightweight World Championship
programme.desc: This under 105kg category event is the ultimate preparation for up-and-coming strongman athletes before entering the heavy class. The Lightweight World Championship is a special every year in the SCL calendar as it sees new talents rise and many promising athletes who are gearing up for future tournaments. A total of 25 athletes from 16 different countries make their way to Kokkola, Finland

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E11 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 11, Romania
programme.desc: Situated in the very heart of the Carpathian Mountains, Sibiu is a Romanian town where the climate is pleasantly mild, offering some of the best weather conditions for a strongman event around Europe. All this, without doubt, set the mood for the high results and showtime vibes in Stage 11 of Strongman Champions League. The competition in Sibiu was organized in six different disciplines

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E12 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 12, Curacao
programme.desc: From now on every stage of these series will be more than crucial. Curacao is a beautiful Dutch island in the Caribbean, with a great atmosphere to hold another stage of the MLO Strongman Champions League. Let’s see who takes the title here and who will secure a place in the next stage.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E13 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 13, Jordan
programme.desc: Ten of the world’s strongest men gathered in Amman to compete in Jordan’s first-ever Truck-Pull Championship. The contestants race against the clock while pulling a 21-ton truck across the track. One of the most fierce competitors to take part in the event was four-time winner of the World’s Strongest Man competition, Brian Shaw.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E14 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 14, Greece
programme.desc: Taking place in Corinth, Greece, considered by many the cradle of the sports competition games, an epic strongman battle will mark the last stage before the upcoming big two-day season’s finale in Chetumal, Mexico. In front of more than 5000 spectators, the twelve athletes compete in Log Lifts, Card Deadlift, Conan’s Wheel and Loading.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E15 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 15, Mexico World Finals (Part 1)
programme.desc: The first day of the two-part finale sees the strongest men competing in Carry and Drag, Dumbbell Lift and the Truck Pull. Everything is possible in this heated fight for the crown against the backdrop of stunning Chetumal, Mexico.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E16 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 16, Mexico World Finals (Part 2)
programme.desc: On the second day of the grand finale of the 2017 Strongman Champions League, the athletes have a last chance to secure the medals in the spectacular four events Weight for Height, Deadlift Cars, Forward Hold and The Loading Medley. Be prepared for stunning performances – and even world records!

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E01 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 1, Norway - World Strongest Viking
programme.desc: Season 2018 begins with 14 strongest men in the world, all competing for the title. The competition kicks off in Norway. We’ll see typical Viking disciplines, team events and world records in heavy conditions in the land of snow and ice. They will suffer, they will freeze and fight in this first competition of the year for the title that they will carry on their shoulders throughout whole year.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E02 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 2, Germany - FIBO Power
programme.desc: The next stop in strongest league of the world is muscle capital, largest number of strong shoulders per capichampions league on the planet. It’s a FIBO - the biggest expo on planet Earth and the second stage of 2018 Strongman champions league, in Cologne, Germany.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E03 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 3, Abu Dhabi
programme.desc: For the first time in history, Strongman Champions League will set up competition in Abu Dhabi. The line-up of super athletes, who are part of the SCL, includes former world champions Dainis Zageris (Latvia) and Krzysztof Radzikowski (Poland), current world champion Matjaz Belsak (Slovenia) and biggest strongman in the World Sean O’Hagan (Ireland).

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E04 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 4, Holland (Part 1)
programme.desc: Strongman classic in land where there is no place for anything else excepts strength, fight and endurance. Here are fourteen of the strongest men, fighting for the title of strongest in Holland.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E05 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 5, Holland (Part 2)
programme.desc: We go back to Holland, where former champion Dainis Zageris is in leading position after the first three events. Alongside Radzikowski, he is in this moment favorite for world title, and also leader shirt holder.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E06 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 6, Finland
programme.desc: Stage six of Strongman champions league, 2018 is set back on north, in Finland. Here we have Matjaz Belsak, wearing SCL leader shirt, one of the biggest strongman in the World Mika Torro, fan favorite strongman in all over the World – Will Baggott, and also big name from Baltic – Aivars Smaukstelis

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E07 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 7, Serbia
programme.desc: Twelve strongman, including defending Worldchampion Matjaz Belsak from Slovenia , will compete on “Air spa” for the title of best in homeland country of Tesla, Pupin, Novak Djokovic. Matjaz Belsak is the SCL leader in this competition, chasing his third victory this season.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E08 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 8, Finland - U105 (Part 1)
programme.desc: The World championship in lightweights of the Strongman Champions League bring to us 50 strongmen from all over the world. All athletes are under 105 kilograms and for them this is the step up to the ultimate heavyweights.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E09 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 9, Finland - U105 (Part 2)
programme.desc: In this second stage of the World championship of lightweights we will find out who out of the 12 athletes will win the title in the under 105 kilogram category.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E10 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 10, Romania (Part 1)
programme.desc: The first part of SCL Romania 2018 will be hosted in Brasov. This episode features a new event for Strongman Champion League: “ The Chopper Pull”!

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E11 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 11, Romania (Part 2)
programme.desc: After three classical Strongman events – Dead lift, Loading and Front hold – and one historical, Chopper Pull for the first time in history of Strongman, now we go to find out who will take title in Romania. This is the second stage in Romania and it remains to be seen who will win the title; Aivars, Travis or Krzyzstof?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E12 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 12, Curacao (Part 1)
programme.desc: The next destination of Strongman Champions League is in a piece of paradise on earth – Curacao. We bring to you some special Strongman events like the Rock Lift, Tug of War and Weight for Height in this episode.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E13 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 13, Curacao (Part 2)
programme.desc: This is the last competition before the grand finals. After the first three events Zageris is in top place, but can O’Hagan, Baggott, Petursson and Ortmayer step into the final? Last chance some of them will find through events like Forward Hold, Truck Pull, Dead Lift and loading very big objects.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E14 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 14, Road to Mexico
programme.desc: We bring you 50 minutes of Strongman inside. Fears, inspiration, courage, the best and worst from our finalists and their expectation of the finals. We also go to Poland and Germany to represent one day in the training of Krzysztof Radzikowski and Dennis Kohlruss. See all the finalists for Mexico in their comfort zone here, with their backgrounds /motivations /family and friends.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E15 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 15, Mexico - World Finals (Part 1)
programme.desc: The first part of the Strongman Champions League 2018 finals in Mexico. The last twelve athletes all pushing their boundaries and testing their limits to take the World title.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E16 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 16, Mexico - World Finals (Part 2)
programme.desc: After 11 months and 14 competitions all over the world, it all comes down to the final in this episode. The strongmen must show their best skills and every mistake is expensive, so their concentration must be at the highest possible level. Will Krzysztof manage to take off back or will Dainis maintain his lead?

programme.title: Keep Austin Weird
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Basic Versus Baller: Travel at Any Cost
programme.desc: In the state capital of Texas, Marko and Alex see what Austin has to offer. An eclectic city known for its music and cuisine, the guys brave the Texas heat and check out what keeps Austin weird.

programme.title: Levels of Luxury in Laos
programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 Basic Versus Baller: Travel at Any Cost
programme.desc: Sandwiched between Thailand, Vietnam, and Cambodia, Laos is a destination often overlooked by tourists. Marko and Alex are uncovering the hidden gem of Vientiane, the capital city, to see what goes on in this sleepy town beside the Mekong River.

programme.title: The Gainful Grace of Geneva
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 Basic Versus Baller: Travel at Any Cost
programme.desc: Marko and Alex find themselves in the prosperous and pristine city of Geneva, Switzerland. A city nestled alongside a beautiful glacier-fed lake, the guys will explore the riches Geneva has to offer.

programme.title: Tacos, Brats, and Biscuits in Austin
programme.desc: Frankie goes to Austin for breakfast tacos, sizzlin’ sausage, loaded biscuits, and decadent dessert pancakes.

programme.title: Smash Burgers and A Slice in Los Angeles
programme.desc: Frankie tries the best bites in LA: a classic Mexican place, a donut spot, pizza to-go, and a fab burger joint.

programme.title: Pierogies, Bagels, and Ramen in NYC
programme.desc: Frankie Celenza hits NYC as he samples warm bagels, pillowy pierogies, innovative ice cream, and real ramen.

programme.title: Brooklyn’s Best Pizza Tour
programme.desc: Frankie tries the best Brooklyn pizza from Neo-Neapolitan to coal oven pies, new toppings, and Italian classics.

programme.title: BBQ Bowls and Puffy Tacos in San Antonio
programme.desc: Frankie Celenza tries San Antonio’s best brunch, epic puffy tacos, colorful conchitas, and BBQ Thai curry bowls.

programme.title: Loaded Dogs and Classic Cocktails in San Diego
programme.desc: Frankie Celenza heads to San Diego to try modern latkes, loaded hot dogs, frosty snow ice, and French cocktails.

programme.title: Game Day

programme.title: Transference
programme.desc: Josh on aina varuillaan ja vainoharhojen vallassa. Han elaa hyvin rasittavaa elamaa, koska pitaa hairiintynytta sisartaan piilossa salaisessa bunkkerissa. Han yrittaa pitaa sisaren yliluonnolliset voimat salassa muulta maailmalta. Kun sisar akkia sairastuu, Josh joutuu turvautumaan tiedemiehen apuun saadakseen sisarensa terveeksi. Kohtalokas paatos aiheuttaa sen, etta sisaren supervoimat paljastuvat.

programme.title: Alien Code
